# App shell & empty states

## Tab-root scaffold

All main tabs share the same shell so content floats above the glass nav island:

```dart
Scaffold(
  extendBody: true,
  backgroundColor: Colors.transparent,
  appBar: AppBar(title: TriftlyAppBarTitle(title: '…')),
  body: …,
)
```

| Tab | Page | App bar actions |
|-----|------|-----------------|
| Explore | `explore_page.dart` | — |
| Trips | `trip_list_page.dart` | `+` create trip, notifications |
| Spend | `spend_page.dart` | — |
| Tools | `tools_page.dart` | title-only |
| Me | `profile_page.dart` | settings |

- **Do not** set an opaque `Scaffold.backgroundColor` on tab roots — `scaffold_with_nav_bar.dart` paints the gradient.
- List padding: use `AppSpacing.listBottomInset(context)` when content scrolls behind the nav island.
- **Trip detail** is different: use `GlassIconButton` / `GlassToggle` in the app bar (see `liquid-glass-ui.mdc`), not plain `IconButton` clusters.

## Empty-state decision tree

Pick the lightest pattern that fits the slot:

```
Full tab / list has zero items?
  └─ YES → EmptyState (centered icon + title + optional subtitle + CTA)
           Examples: Trips phase filter, Spend wallet error, global Spend no trips

Trip sub-tab with no data yet (Map / Plan day / etc.)?
  └─ YES → Does the tab need a visual preview or cross-tab link?
           ├─ YES → Glass hero empty (MapEmptyState, MapDayEmptyState, MapUnmappedHero)
           │        Use SpendGlassShell / MapPreviewGraphic; primary CTA links to Plan or action
           └─ NO  → TripInlineEmptyCard (Plan day slot, compact suggestions + optional action)
                    Standard AppCard, emoji header, suggestion chips

Metric / summary slot with $0?
  └─ YES → Glass metric card with compact badge — NOT a paragraph empty state
           Examples: SpendOverviewMetricCard, "$0 spent", badge "No expenses"
           See liquid-glass-ui.mdc

Inline stat hint on Plan (today spending)?
  └─ YES → Pill strip (_TodaySpendInlineStrip) — never a glass island

Expense rows / ledger lists?
  └─ Empty list body only — overview row still shows $0 glass cards above
```

| Widget | When |
|--------|------|
| `EmptyState` | Whole-page or full-list empties (Trips, Spend wallet, errors) |
| `TripInlineEmptyCard` | In-flow day/slot placeholders with quick-add suggestions |
| `MapEmptyState` / `MapDayEmptyState` | Map tab — glass preview + Plan link |
| `PlanDayEmptyState` | Plan day with no spots — emoji grid + quick ideas |
| `SpendOverviewMetricCard` + badge | Spend tab $0 — no `SpendEmptyState` hero block |

## Global Spend (`3_spend/` + `spend_shared/`)

Personal wallet across trips — distinct from trip-detail Spend tab glass metrics.

| Widget | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `SpendWalletCard` | Global wallet hero — `SpendGlassShell` + shared metric typography (not teal gradient blocks) |
| `SpendSectionTitle` | Section label + optional count (Trips, Balances, Recent) |
| `SpendListCard` | Bordered list surface for trip rows and activity |
| `SpendWalletTripRow` | Single trip row inside `SpendListCard` |
| `SpendExpenseDetailSheet` | Utility sheet (pattern B) before navigating to trip Spend |

- Phase filter: reuse `TripPhaseSegment` like Trips list.
- Pull-to-refresh on `SpendOverviewBloc`.
- Global wallet hero uses the same `SpendGlassShell` as trip Spend metrics — see `liquid-glass-ui.mdc`.
- Trip-detail Spend metrics: see `liquid-glass-ui.mdc`.

## Sheets in Spend shared

- Open with `TriftlyBottomSheet.show` — not raw `showModalBottomSheet`.
- Read-only detail sheets: `SheetScaffold` + `SheetSectionHeader` + `SheetSoftCard` + `SheetPrimaryButton` (pattern B).

